<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="274" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,1482,1727]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1591,1617]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">Remarks.</emphasis>
First records from 
<collectingCountry box="[526,635,1591,1617]" name="Mongolia" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">Mongolia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[686,788,1591,1617]" name="Slovakia" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">Slovakia</collectingCountry>
. This species is widely distributed in the Palaearctic region (
<bibRefCitation author="Yu, D. S. &amp; van Achterberg, C. &amp; Horstmann, K." box="[158,321,1627,1653]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274" refId="ref7112" refString="Yu, D. S., van Achterberg, C. &amp; Horstmann, K. (2016) Taxapad 2016, Ichneumonoidea 2015. Nepean, Ontario. Database on flash-drive. Available from: http: // www. taxapad. com" type="url" year="2016">
Yu 
<emphasis box="[198,247,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
). The Slovakian records were already reported by 
<bibRefCitation author="Zilahi-Kiss, A." box="[881,1090,1627,1653]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274" pagination="32 - 146" refId="ref7157" refString="Zilahi-Kiss, A. (1924) Beitrag zur Kenntnis der ungarischen und siebenburgischen Ichneumoniden- (Schlupfwespen-) Fauna. Verhandlungen und Mitteilungen des Siebenburgischen Vereins fur Naturwissenschaften in Hermannstadt, 72 - 74, 32 - 146." type="journal article" year="1924">Zilahi-Kiss (1924)</bibRefCitation>
, based on the same specimens; however, these records apparently remained unknown and were not incorporated by more recent catalogues, which list this species as not known from 
<collectingCountry box="[546,644,1699,1725]" name="Slovakia" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">Slovakia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Sedivy, J." box="[658,804,1699,1727]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274" pagination="1 - 194" refId="ref6754" refString="Sedivy, J. (1989) Enumeration insectorum Bohemoslovakiae. Check list of Czechoslovak insects III (Hymenoptera). Acta Faunistica Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae, 19, 1 - 194." type="journal article" year="1989">Šedivý 1989</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Yu, D. S. &amp; van Achterberg, C. &amp; Horstmann, K." box="[814,975,1699,1725]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274" refId="ref7112" refString="Yu, D. S., van Achterberg, C. &amp; Horstmann, K. (2016) Taxapad 2016, Ichneumonoidea 2015. Nepean, Ontario. Database on flash-drive. Available from: http: // www. taxapad. com" type="url" year="2016">
Yu 
<emphasis box="[852,902,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="274">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Holy, K. &amp; Zeman, V." box="[986,1224,1699,1725]" pageId="6" pageNumber="274" pagination="5 - 119" refId="ref6193" refString="Holy, K. &amp; Zeman, V. (2018) Catalogue of Ichneumonidae (Hymenoptera) of the Czech and Slovak Republics. Acta Musei Moraviae, Scientiae biologicae, 103 (1), 5 - 119." type="journal article" year="2018">Holý &amp; Zeman 2018</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
